                            <h3 class="mb-4">What is UI UX?</h3>
                            <p class="mb-5">UI refers to the screens, buttons, toggles, icons, and other visual elements that you interact with when using a website, app, or other electronic devices. UX refers to the entire interaction you have with a product, including how you feel about the interaction.</p>
